nodes.text: Sabre Eight was the call sign that was used by a person during an operation on the planet Cularin.

During the time of the Clone Wars, Sabre Eight participated in a Cularin Militia operation to attack the Wyrd, a group of Tarasin witches, in the jungles of Cularin. However, Sabre Eight was attacked by the Wyrd and sent out a message on his comm set to Sabre Hilt, before being killed. The Wyrd then took the comm set from his body.
